data.description: DESIRABLE LOCATION. Very spacious & move in ready. Modern design with high ceilings. Fully tiled first floor, high quality scratch resistant laminate on second level open concept. Great room features bright natural light with beautiful view to the outdoors. Lots of windows. Spacious primary includes high quality, built-in wood closets. Owner's suite bath features dual sinks, glass enclosed shower, separate garden tub & private water closet. Expansive community pool with loads of sitting areas, lounge chairs & restrooms. Exceptional A-graded schools. Davie is an Equestrian community with horse trails close by. This property is conveniently located close to I-595 and I-75 making north, south, east & west very accessible. Ft. Lauderdale Airport, Parks & Beaches all a short drive away.
